<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=2>• extensive knowledge and experience with BusinessWorks, BusinessConnect, BusinessEvents, Adapters, EMS, Hawk, and Rendezvous.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>
