<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=2>• an individual with experience troubleshooting and resolving problems related to TIBCO applications.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>
